      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration experts and parts seekers! This vehicle is ready for a second life in the hands of someone who knows their way around a garage. While it currently requires extensive mechanical work and body repairs, it serves as a fantastic, low-cost opportunity for a dedicated project or a valuable source of components. Grab this diamond in the rough and bring your vision to life!",
