    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a major restoration project. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission and an engine that requires a complete overhaul to run reliably. The body shows extensive wear with rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and peeling clear coat across most surfaces. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn and the electronics are largely non-functional. It is being sold strictly as-is and will need to be towed.",
