    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, it starts and runs consistently, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid option for someone needing dependable transportation who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
