    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it still runs like a total dream! I've taken great care of it over the years, so it's officially ready for its next big adventure with you. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come by and take it for a spin, you're going to love it!",
